name: Family Management Game In Immortal Continent
summary:
WARNING: This novel is a hidden gem! Don't be fooled by the cliché sypnosis!
Read 20 chapters before deciding!
***This novel is also in the Webnovel app with the same name. (More chapters are uploaded there for now.)***
Li Wei accidentally obtained a simulator that allowed him to manage a family of cultivators. He discovered that the descendants in the game would offer him strange and unique sacrifices.
"Thanks to the ancestor for the gift, our family has become the most powerful family!"
"Hurry up and offer a sacrifice to the ancestor. Please accept this spiritual weapon!"
"Ancestor, we have already conquered the immortal world!"
Then, one day, the descendants of the Li family, who had been in the game, appeared on Earth in grand flying boats. Under the astonished eyes of the entire world, these descendants paid homage to Li Wei in great numbers.
"Welcome our ancestor home!"
author: darktea
